## 1. Project Overview
This assignment demonstrates the creation of a `FoodItems` database for a restaurant. The goal is to manage various non-veg categories (Chicken, Mutton, Fish, Prawns) and perform data retrieval using logical and arithmetic operators.

---

## 2. Database Schema & Data Insertion

```sql
-- Creating the Table
CREATE TABLE FoodItems (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT,       -- Unique ID for each food item
    name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,              -- Name of the food item
    category VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,           -- Chicken, Mutton, Fish, Prawns
    price DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,            -- Price of the item
    type ENUM('Veg','Non-Veg') NOT NULL      -- Food type
);

-- Inserting Records (Humanized Sample Data)
